Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohle je klíč do Zlaté Země!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.07,0:21:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohle je...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.05,0:21:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to tu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Opravdu existuje...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:21:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otcovo zlato!
